test_even_range:
assert [46, 48, 50] == [48]
  At index 0 diff: 46 != 48
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 48
  Full diff:
  - [48]
  + [46, 48, 50]
test_large_range:
assert [23, 24, 25] == [24]
  At index 0 diff: 23 != 24
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 24
  Full diff:
  - [24]
  + [23, 24, 25]
